text: "Reelin' In the Years" is a 1973 song by Steely Dan. It was taken from their debut studio album Can't Buy a Thrill. It went to number 11 in the United States, number 15 in Canada and number 62 in Australia. It did not chart in the United Kingdom and New Zealand. ==References== Category:1973 songs Category:Steely Dan songs Category:Jazz rock songs
